articles.title: AirAsia KL-Kuching tickets drop below RM200 after Sarawak authorities approve more flights - The Star Online
articles.description: PETALING JAYA: AirAsia has dropped the price of flight tickets to Kuching from Kuala Lumpur to under RM200, from about RM1,000 previously, for a one-way trip ahead of the Dec 18 Sarawak state election and Christmas.
